><em>本周：扎克·布莱恩 (Zach Bryan) 发行新专辑，展现了不可否认的明星效应；赛琳娜·戈麦斯 (Selena Gomez) 和麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus) 同步发行了单曲；G-Eazy 帮助粉丝在社交媒体等方面闪回不同的时间。</em></p><h2 class="heading larva //   a-font-primary-bold-xl   "><strong>扎克·布莱恩 (Zach Bryan) 成功收购流媒体</strong></h2><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy" class="youtube-player" width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZVVvJjwzl6c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent" allowfullscreen="true" style="border:0;" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation"></iframe></div></figure><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>在<em>公告牌</em>排行榜上，夏季结束时，一位男性乡村艺术家再次达到了新的商业高度，这是很合适的。扎克·布莱恩 (Zach Bryan) 为摩根·沃伦 (Morgan Wallen)、卢克·库姆斯 (Luke Combs)、杰森·阿尔丁 (Jason Aldean) 和奥利弗·安东尼 (Oliver Anthony) 的这一季的成功故事画上了圆满的句号。如果早期流媒体数据良好，扎克·布莱恩 (Zach Bryan) 将于上周五（8 月 25 日）发行后，凭借他的同名新专辑首次亮相。 ——尤其是凯西·马斯格雷夫斯的二重唱“我记得一切”——就是一些迹象。<br><br>根据 Luminate 的数据，包含 16 首歌曲的扎克·<em>布莱恩 (Zach Bryan)</em>在发行之日在美国的点播流量就达到了 5440 万次，虽然在接下来的几天里其日流量有所下降，但去年<em>《美国心碎》</em> (American Heartbreak) 的后续流量已经清除到周日结束时，总播放量已达到九位数，到周一结束时，播放量已接近 1.47 亿。与此同时，布莱恩和马斯格雷夫斯讲述了一段早已逝去的浪漫的《I Remember Everything》成为专辑在流媒体服务上的突破歌曲，在发行的前四天里就获得了 1810 万次点播播放。<br><br> 《我记得一切》能爬到多高？在热门 100 强中，布莱恩凭借《Something in the Orange》跻身第 10 位，而马斯格雷夫斯则凭借《Follow Your Arrow》登上了第 60 位，因此两位艺术家都可以凭借同一首歌创下职业生涯新高。去年， <em>《American Heartbreak》</em>在 Billboard 200 排行榜上排名第五，而本周早些时候，布莱恩宣布了 2024 年一系列体育场馆和竞技场的演出日期，他的目标是将自己的目光投向了潜在的排行榜第一名。 <em>– 杰森·利普舒茨</em></p><hr class="separator larva // lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-margin-l-00 u-width-135 lrv-u-margin-tb-00 u-width-100p  " /><h2 class="heading larva //   a-font-primary-bold-xl   "><strong>麦莉在迪士尼明星单曲对决中领先赛琳娜</strong></h2><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy" class="youtube-player" width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IZ3XMOdOdKM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent" allowfullscreen="true" style="border:0;" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation"></iframe></div></figure><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>当流行音乐界人士注意到流行歌星赛琳娜·戈麦斯 (Selena Gomez) 和麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus)（曾因分别在 00 年代迪士尼青少年节目<em>《Wizards of Waverly Place</em> 》和<em>《Hannah Montana》</em>中主演而闻名）都在周五（8 月 25 日）发行新单曲时，自然而然地激发了老粉丝之间的竞争精神。艺术家们在社交媒体上展现了自己的风格， <a  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.email.billboard.com%2F%3Fqs%3Dff14deaafe82d470d05c6bb32e74c9bdc6f8ec966c9230a2a6dd5af2ca8d1930878e9c91b8b47353e69a90cecffec793fb5ea3922aeac0df&#038;data=05%7C01%7Candrew.unterberger%40billboard.com%7C45eb2866658540273a6308dba99a14e6%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638290251472214455%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=4KIkbJulap%2FSlVF%2Fx2SBNfvHh%2BWLSN1NM%2BARS%2Btu9aU%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  >赛勒斯转发了</a>她的一位粉丝分享的一段视频，她和戈麦斯在<em>《汉娜·蒙塔娜》</em>的旧剧集中互相吐槽，其中后者客串出演，并附上了这样的信息：“@selenagomez 和我都放弃了我们的生活。”即将推出新单曲……我说我们#USEDTOBEYOUNG。” （“Single Soon”和“Used to Be Young”分别是戈麦斯和赛勒斯新专辑的名称。）<br><br>好吧，早期回归已经到来，到目前为止，赛勒斯的《Young》在销量和流量方面都领先于戈麦斯的《单曲》。根据 Luminate 的数据，在发行的前四天里，《Young》在美国的官方点播流媒体播放次数已超过 1040 万次，数字歌曲销量超过 15,000 首，而《Single》的流媒体播放次数超过 810 万次，销量接近 6,400 首。分别领先 28% 和 144%。 （两人都将在下周的百强单曲榜前半部分首次亮相，尽管他们可能会被布莱恩和马斯格雷夫斯更响亮的鞠躬所掩盖。）<br><br>他们并不是仅有的两位可能在下周夺得排行榜冠军的从儿童电视到成人流行音乐的跨界明星。前 Nickelodeon <em>Victorious</em>和<em>Sam &amp; Cat</em>演员 Ariana Grande 在 2013 年首张专辑<em>《Yours Truly》</em>发行 10 周年之际也迎来了巨大的销量增长，她通过豪华重新发行专辑和一系列纪念活动来纪念这张专辑。周五，该专辑在美国的官方点播播放量猛增至近 340 万次，比上周五（323,000 次）猛增 946%。 –<em>安德鲁·安特伯格</em></p><hr class="separator larva // lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-margin-l-00 u-width-135 lrv-u-margin-tb-00 u-width-100p  " /><h2 class="heading larva //   a-font-primary-bold-xl   "> <strong>G-Eazy 的“Tumblr Girls”掀起了 TikTok 怀旧浪潮</strong></h2><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy" class="youtube-player" width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fu7NR1qe_Mk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent" allowfullscreen="true" style="border:0;" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation"></iframe></div></figure><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>“第一视角：现在是 2014 年，你 8 岁了，看到所有十几岁的女孩穿着星巴克、粉红色和条纹短上衣，你希望自己是个青少年！”两周前，一名 TikTok 用户在一段自己在卧室里闲逛的视频中<a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40cooljizz%2Fvideo%2F7267259034254773509&#038;data=05%7C01%7Candrew.unterberger%40billboard.com%7Ce5cefffd4ae0409764c508dba980cd7c%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638290142916147347%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=hwwFSWBko%2FJ5tO1eVl%2BA5%2FFuLFTLyTDHSK%2F0B2FrmkM%3D&#038;reserved=0"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >发布了</a>这个标题，并获得了 77 万个赞和 5,000 条评论；青春期记忆的配乐是 G-Eazy 2014 年由 Christoph Andersson 演唱的歌曲《Tumblr Girls》，最近几周，随着 TikTok 用户回顾 2010 年代中期的记忆，这首歌已成为一首怀旧歌曲。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> G-Eazy actually isn&#39;t featured in the trending part of the song; instead, it&#39;s the song&#39;s outro – crooned by the rapper&#39;s frequent studio collaborator Andersson, with the lines “Never knew her name, they&#39;re looking all the same to me/ They only chase the fame, there&#39;s no one left to blame but me” – being highlighted in TikTok clips. As more videos of 2014 flashbacks accumulate, “Tumblr Girls” has shot up in overall listens, with weekly streams basically quadrupling from 552,000 the week ending Aug. 10 to 2.25 million two weeks later, according to Luminate.</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> “Tumblr Girls” never charted upon its debut, but it&#39;s become a fan favorite — so much so that two years ago, G-Eazy released a sequel, “Running Wild (Tumblr Girls 2),” although TikTok has yet to scoop that one up in the same way. <em>– JL</em> </p><hr class="separator larva // lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-margin-l-00 u-width-135 lrv-u-margin-tb-00 u-width-100p  " /><h2 class="heading larva //   a-font-primary-bold-xl   "> <strong>Beyoncé&#39;s “XO” Gets Streams &#39;Turned&#39; Up by Teen TV Sensation</strong> </h2><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy" class="youtube-player" width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3xUfCUFPL-8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent" allowfullscreen="true" style="border:0;" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation"></iframe></div></figure><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>We&#39;ve written plenty on <em>Billboard</em> about the <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/taylor-swift-august-charts-summer-i-turned-pretty-trailer/"  >extensive</a> <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/taylor-swift-exile-summer-i-turned-pretty-finale-fans-react-1235395339/"  >artistic</a> <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/taylor-swift-back-to-december-taylors-version-summer-i-turned-pretty-trailer-1235364688/"  >partnership</a> Amazon Prime&#39;s hit coming-of-age drama <em>The Summer I Turned Pretty</em> has developed with Taylor Swift, having featured over a dozen of Swift&#39;s songs across its two seasons. But the show&#39;s second season proved that it can also deploy the music of another pop icon currently on a globe-conquering world tour: Beyoncé, whose 2014 classic “XO” is featured in the finale&#39;s climactic scene, resolving the long-building love triangle between the characters Belly (Lola Tung) and brothers Jeremiah (Gavin Casalegno) and and Conrad (Christopher Briney).</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> The scene had an unsurprising impact on viewers, who then proceeded to stream the <em>Beyoncé</em> self-titled ballad en masse. The song jumped from 388,000 official on-demand streams for the tracking week ending Aug. 17 (the day before the finale was released to streaming) to nearly 990,000 streams for the following week – a jump of 155%, according to Luminate. With <em>Summer</em> already having been renewed for a third season, you can bet that pop stars of all shapes and sizes will be angling to get a prime sync on the Prime smash. – <em>AU</em> </p><hr class="separator larva // lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-margin-l-00 u-width-135 lrv-u-margin-tb-00 u-width-100p  " /><h2 class="heading larva //   a-font-primary-bold-xl   "> <strong>Q&amp;A: Christine Rogerson, SVP of Business Operations at Vibee, on What&#39;s Trending Up in Her World</strong></h2><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <strong>A very hectic season in the live industry is coming to a close. What was Vibee&#39;s focus over the summer?</strong></p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Vibee spent the summer hosting and engaging with our fans at several festival integrations like Lollapalooza in Chicago, Day Trip in Long Beach, TidalWave in Atlantic City, and BeachIt! in Virginia Beach. We were also in the thick of our planning processes for the monumental U2: UV Achtung Baby Live at Sphere run of shows in Las Vegas, Lionel Richie&#39;s Dancing on the Sand in the Bahamas, the inaugural EDSea cruise, and Tiesto&#39;s Chasing Sunsets in Cabo San Lucas.</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <strong>Can you speak a little bit about the newly announced</strong> <a  href="https://u2.vibee.com/"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  ><strong>immersive U2 fan portal</strong></a> <strong>and what attendees can expect?</strong></p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Fans are in for a real treat with the Zoo Station fan portal. The portal was developed by Vibee in collaboration with Gavin Friday, who is U2&#39;s longtime creative director, and with insight and input from the band. Fans will move throughout 12,000 square feet of immersive exhibits over two floors. Key attractions include the incredible Anton Corbijn Gallery featuring photos and videos from the famed photographer as well as the Zoo Station Cinema which is curated by The Edge himself! For those fans who love memorabilia, the U2 Pop-Up Shop will be a must visit with a variety of collectibles, including a capsule collection of limited edition exclusive U2:UV items. It&#39;s truly a special experience for newer or those dedicated fans of U2.</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <strong>What industry-wide trends did you notice this summer in terms of the evolution of immersive fan experiences?</strong></p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Right now, fans are still prioritizing entertainment and travel in their personal budgets but, as discretionary dollars become more precious, we have to ensure that we are presenting people with standout experiences that meet or exceed their needs and expectations on multiple levels. People are looking for memory-making opportunities and bucket list moments. As a destination experience company, Vibee is seeking out those ways that we can engage with fans, curate an experience, weave in a story, and connect great music with amazing destinations. The feedback that we received from fans is that they were searching out those unique experiences and shared moments at the events that they were able to attend. We aim to deliver on that.</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <strong>Fill in the blank: in the next few years, concertgoers will be surprised by ______.</strong></p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> …the ways in which immersive experiences continue to enhance live music events, which is exactly what Vibee is committed to accomplishing through our artist partnerships, thoughtful curation, destination selection, and bespoke inclusions. – <em>JL</em></p></div> ;
